name: tomato
description:
I am a tomato, I have been a tomato since I can remember And I always tried to be the best tomato And seeing other tomatoes, I was motivated to grow and be the best Until I was in a place and time of this world Which led me to enter another perspective, The image you see is me with one of my kind Which was neither the best nor grown But now we are together in smaller pieces Suspended in an atmosphere full of a Fiery
substance called oil In the arms of the big and small bubbles that surround us And it's amazing that we do not know what we will become but we are sure of change.
